    ‚ąá result‚ÜźCreateTodo req;title;todo
      :Access Public Instance
      :If {0::1 ‚čĄ 0=‚ćĶ.‚éēNC‚äā'title'}req.Payload
          req.Fail 400
          result‚Üź'<div class="error">Title is required</div>' #.Render.RespondHTML req
